## Installation

After installing via Chocolatey, you can start LaxyFile by running:

```
laxyfile
```

For AI features, set your OpenRouter API key:

```
set OPENROUTER_API_KEY=your-api-key
laxyfile
```

## System Requirements

- Windows 10 or later
- Python 3.8 or higher (automatically installed)
- Modern terminal with color support (Windows Terminal recommended)

